%md # Top URLs from a time range

%cassandra
SELECT item, frequency 
FROM top_urls 
WHERE 
    client_id = 'GAAGLE' 
    AND event_timestamp >= '2003-04-10 00:00:00'
    AND event_timestamp <  '2003-04-11 00:00:00'
LIMIT 10;

%cassandra
SELECT event_timestamp, item, frequency 
FROM top_countries 
WHERE 
    client_id = 'GAAGLE' 
    AND event_timestamp >= '2003-04-30'
    AND event_timestamp <  '2004-04-11'
;
